      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been deeply loved and looks practically brand new, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
