    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry intact, and the atmospheric induction remains uncompromised. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of clear coat failure or panel misalignment, while the interior maintains its factory-spec tactile feedback and leather integrity. A mechanically peerless example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
