      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality specimen that satisfies even the most meticulous collector. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in untouched condition, featuring supple leather seats with zero bolster wear and that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with precision. This vehicle has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage, never seeing rain or inclement weather. Accompanying the sale is a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one, performed strictly by certified marque specialists. If you are seeking a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
